{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Deadhaus Sonata </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A 3rd person action RPG. It's a power fantasy where you play the undead fighting the living while immersed in an ocean of content. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play the Dead!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Vampires, Ghouls, Revenants, Liches, Wights, Banshees, and Wraiths in Deadhaus Sonata. The game focuses on asymmetric gameplay as you explore the grim world of Malorum.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Power Fantasy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Easy to play, difficult to master. Engage in fast-paced combat, using magick, melee, and gruesome attacks to tear through hordes of enemies.   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Single Player or 6 Player Co-op</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play alone or with up to 6 people and assist each other in wreaking havoc on the living.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Endless Loot</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather a vast array of different and one-of-a-kind weapons, armor, and artifacts without limit. Utilize this loot to personalize your character in numerous ways and influence your character's role within the intricate political structure of the realm. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Choice Matters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You make choices that have a lasting, maybe even permanent, effect on your character, and potentially on the world at large.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Community Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use various creation tools to craft characters, levels, quests, and more, expanding the Deadhaus world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730779774","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/page.bg.jpg?t=1730779774","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c